      • getCooldownExpiry

        java.util.Optional<java.time.Instant> getCooldownExpiry()
        Specifies when the next redemption opportunity is.
        • If isSuccess() is true, this returns the next time the Kit can be redeemed by the player.
        • Else, if there is still a cooldown attached to this kit and player, the next time this kit may be redeemed.
        Returns:
        The Instant redemption may next happen, if a cooldown is currently in effect.
